ractices|journal=Journal of Applied Computer Science Methods|date=2012|volume=4|issue=2|pages=5–20|doi=10.2478/jacsm|url=http://yadda.icm.edu.pl/yadda/element/bwmeta1.element.baztech-85fc9fd0-80a6-48b2-84a4-62820e8e1bf2}}</ref>
