'''Vedantam Ramalinga Sastry''' is an [[Indian classical dance | Indian classical dancer]] in [[Kuchipudi]]. He won the Sangeet Natak Akademi award in 2013 for his research on Kuchipudi dance form.<ref>http://www.thehindu.com/features/friday-review/dance/where-an-exquisite-art-evolved/article2301980.ece</ref> He is the Principal of Siddhendra Yogi Kuchipudi Kalapeetham.<ref>http://www.hindu.com/2008/09/18/stories/2008091850560200.htm</ref><ref>http://www.hindu.com/2009/03/31/stories/2009033151130200.htm</ref>

